Grimlock looked back at Slag. "We Dinobots, We don't fight SLag, save it
for wussy Autobots who cant fight. If they to weak we take over" he said
back at his long time friend. He knew how much they all wanted to beat
the tar out of something, after remaining inactive for so long.
